org.openimaj.experiment.annotations

Annotation Type Experiment


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface Experiment
    Annotation for describing an instance of a RunnableExperiment. The information provided by the annotation is used to fill in the ExperimentContext when the experiment is run with a ExperimentRunner.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
